==English==

===Noun===
'''[[Traditional]] [[Chinese]]'''
# Chinese characters used in the Republic of China (Taiwan), Hong Kong, Macau, Singapore, and also in mainland China prior to script simplification and today for certain purposes.

====Antonyms====
*[[Simplified Chinese]]

